{"tid":1524824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"接畜生？","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T18:21:02.000Z","uid":315580,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6845c1a333bf68c64d31675f8d564c07ecbc7d7","tid":1524824,"uid":315580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:19:50.000Z","msg":"我地要等畜生放工，等佢地放低哂啲gear就打柒班畜生。<br />\n<br />\n所以有冇人知今晚咁大批畜生放工，會係咩形式散。<br />\n佢會留係狗竇到天光先走？ 定按排港鐵送佢地走 定點？<br />\n<br />\nBtw若然有落單狗 ，一定要圍佢，然後踩斷佢哋嘅手指。<br />\n咁樣下次出黎先見唔翻佢地。 唔係嘅話佢地嘅仇恨會發洩係下一次度。 踩唔斷都一定拗斷佢哋手臂或者手指。所以一係唔好正面交鋒，一係就做適當嘅傷害 要有目的。<br />\n<br />\n最後 如果要有政治宣洩，我地油黑果粒大星就可以了 唔好做多左 因為敵人從來得一個 由以前到依家都最鍾意搞內戰分化嘅政黨&mdash;&mdash;共匪。"},{"pid":"7baf8378a8463199580322fe2aa514d47463a24d","tid":1524824,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:21:02.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=74b0895b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=1db0dcf7\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=eab03132\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"}]}